---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import logo from '../assets/logo-dark.svg';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Agent Workflows — Learn to Build AI Agents</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Practical guides on AI agents, MCP, agentic workflows, frameworks, and architecture. Learn to build agents that actually work." />
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #0d0f14;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(13,15,20,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-logo img { height: 28px; }
    .nav-logo span { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; color: #fff; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a { color: #94a3b8; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }
    .nav-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1, #3B82F6);
      color: white !important;
      padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600 !important;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: rgba(107,70,193,0.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(107,70,193,0.4);
      color: #a78bfa;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 40%, #a78bfa);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #94a3b8;
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B46C1, #3B82F6);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      color: #e2e8f0;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

    /* STATS */
    .stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .stat { text-align: center; }
    .stat-value { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; margin-top: 0.2rem; }

    /* SECTIONS */
    section { padding: 5rem 2rem; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #7c3aed;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .section-sub { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

    /* CARDS */
    .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      display: block;
    }
    .card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(107,70,193,0.4);
      background: rgba(107,70,193,0.07);
    }
    .card-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* FEATURE HIGHLIGHT */
    .highlight {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .highlight { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .highlight-text h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .highlight-text p { color: #94a3b8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .code-block {
      background: #0a0c10;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Fira Code', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #94a3b8;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .code-block .kw { color: #c084fc; }
    .code-block .fn { color: #60a5fa; }
    .code-block .str { color: #86efac; }
    .code-block .cm { color: #475569; }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    footer a { color: #7c3aed; text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
    <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Agent Workflows" />
    <span>Agent Workflows</span>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/docs/">Docs</a></li>
    <li><a href="/ai-agents/">Agents</a></li>
    <li><a href="/mcp/">MCP</a></li>
    <li><a href="/frameworks/">Frameworks</a></li>
    <li><a href="/docs/" class="nav-cta">Get Started</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-badge">AI Agent Development</div>
  <h1>Build AI agents<br/>that actually work</h1>
  <p>Practical guides on architecture, MCP, frameworks, and patterns. From first agent to production workflows.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="/getting-started/" class="btn-primary">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/ai-agents/" class="btn-secondary">What are AI Agents?</a>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">10+</div><div class="stat-label">Topics Covered</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">4</div><div class="stat-label">Agent Frameworks</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">MCP</div><div class="stat-label">Protocol Guide</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-value">Free</div><div class="stat-label">Always</div></div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="section-label">What you’ll learn</div>
  <h2>Everything to build AI agents</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">From the basics of how agents work to production-ready multi-agent pipelines.</p>
  <div class="cards">
    <a href="/ai-agents/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🤖</div>
      <h3>AI Agents</h3>
      <p>The agent loop, patterns, and when to use agents vs simple AI calls.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/agentic-workflows/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Agentic Workflows</h3>
      <p>Design reliable multi-step AI workflows. The compounding error problem and how to solve it.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/mcp/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🔌</div>
      <h3>MCP</h3>
      <p>Model Context Protocol: connect any agent to any tool. Setup, servers, and building your own.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/frameworks/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">🛠️</div>
      <h3>Frameworks</h3>
      <p>Compare LangChain, CrewAI, and AutoGen. Know when to use each (and when to skip them).</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/agent-instructions/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">📝</div>
      <h3>Agent Instructions</h3>
      <p>CLAUDE.md and the AgentMD pattern. Give your agents persistent context and operating rules.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/code-examples/" class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">💻</div>
      <h3>Code Examples</h3>
      <p>Copy-paste examples: tool-using agents, ReAct loops, MCP clients. Ready to run.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="highlight">
    <div class="highlight-text">
      <div class="section-label">Architecture</div>
      <h2>3-layer agent architecture</h2>
      <p>Separate orchestration from execution. Keep the AI in the coordination layer, not the execution layer. Deterministic code doesn’t compound errors.</p>
      <a href="/agent-instructions/" class="btn-primary">See the pattern</a>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
<span class="cm"># Layer 1: Directives (Markdown SOPs)</span>
directives/job_scraper.md

<span class="cm"># Layer 2: Orchestration (AI Agent)</span>
<span class="cm"># → reads directive, routes to scripts</span>

<span class="cm"># Layer 3: Execution (Python)</span>
<span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">scrape_jobs</span>(query, location):
    <span class="cm"># deterministic, testable</span>
    results = linkedin_api.search(
        query=query,
        location=location
    )
    <span class="kw">return</span> results
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a> + <a href="https://starlight.astro.build">Starlight</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/Sero01/ai-agents-guide">GitHub</a></p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
